{
  "stem": "10835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were given a blanket and a straw filled pillow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were-- there were two rows of bunks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was actually four rows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was front, back, front, back, and tables in the middle, with benches, on which we ate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a kitchen on the same level, and they did the cooking for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the food was very sparse, unsatisfactory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were given-- when we got up in the morning, we were given-- actually, we didn't have breakfast.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were given a container of coffee and a-- a couple of slices of bread, and we took this along with us to-- to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At work, we had a half hour for lunch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, of course, I don't think that maybe they did it on account of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the German and Czech people who worked in the factories, who were at the supervisory capacity, they had to have time for lunch.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we had that food that we brought along with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We each-- we each had-- were given a can in which to put the coffee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And at night, when we ret-- after the day was done, after we returned to-- to the camp, we received a big spoonful of-- of food, which was-- they call it Eintopf, which meant that it's all cooked in one pot.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was mostly vegetables.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Sometimes there were a few pieces of meat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Going back to the work that we did, the work was so dirty that the place was mostly-- you could feel like you were-- like you were in a fog, because it was very dusty.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All that-- that work, that was-- the machine were beating out the dust from the material, it was all-- it all came into the air.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
